title: Year 7 Class 1
text:
Year 7 Class 1 (Korean: 칠학년일반) is a South Korean girl group formed by DRB Entertainment in Seoul, South Korea. The group debuted on January 24, 2014 with "Oppa Virus".


== Members ==
Baek Se-hee (백세희)
Kang Min-ju (강민주)
Shin Ee-rang (신이랑)
Kwon So-jung (권소정)
Han Bit-na (한빛나)
Yoo Hwa (유화)
Go Eun-sil (고은실)
